The Grey;;61;;79;;R;;Following a grueling five-week shift at an Alaskan oil refinery, workers led by sharpshooter John Ottway (Liam Neeson) are flying home for a much-needed vacation. A brutal storm causes their plane to crash in the frozen wilderness, and only eight men (Frank Grillo, Dermot Mulroney), including Ottway, survive. As they trek southward toward civilization and safety, Ottway and his companions must battle mortal injuries, the icy elements, and a pack of hungry wolves.;;Adventure,Drama;;Joe Carnahan;;2012;;Liam Neeson,Frank Grillo,Dermot Mulroney,Dallas Roberts,Joe Anderson,Nonso Anozie,Ben Hernandez Bray,James Badge Dale,Anne Openshaw,Peter Girges,Jonathan James Bitonti,James Bitonti,Ella Kosor,Jacob Blair;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_grey_2012